{"about_the_game":"Nostalgia called, and it wants its pixels back!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051770/extras/Intro.gif?t=1654881236\" /><br><br>Alabama Bones is a classic point and click adventure game, without the convoluted inventory system or pixel hunting. The familiar storyline comes with a twist: you embark on a journey to return decades of stolen artifacts from museums to their rightful owners.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051770/extras/navigation.gif?t=1654881236\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Controls</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mouse - just point and click to move and interact with objects.<br></li><li>Gamepad - move the character close to objets and use the action button to trigger interactions.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051770/extras/cut.gif?t=1654881236\" /><br><br>The first chapter of the game takes us from the Peruvian high desert roads deep into the jungle where our hero needs to find his way back into that one fateful cave. Unfortunately, the cave won't take its secrets back so easily and there will be plenty of unpleasant traps along the way.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051770/extras/fall.gif?t=1654881236\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051770/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1654881236","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051770/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1654881236","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051770/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1654881236","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2051770/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1654881236","categories":[{"description":"Single-playe